  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `PlaybookDispatcher.cs` — locate the point where `DispatchResult` is constructed.</step>
    <step order="2">Identify how the matched playbook's nodes are loaded today; if not loaded, add a load via existing playbook-node repository.</step>
    <step order="3">Identify the "primary AI/DeliverOutput node" — typically the playbook's terminal/output node. Document the selection heuristic in code comment.</step>
    <step order="4">Call `NodeRoutingConfig.Parse(node.ConfigJson)` (Parse handles null gracefully per FR-14f).</step>
    <step order="5">Populate `DispatchResult { ..., NodeDestination = parsed.Destination, WidgetType = parsed.WidgetType }`.</step>
    <step order="6">Add integration test: dispatch `summarize-document-for-workspace` → assert `NodeDestination = Workspace, WidgetType = "structured-output-stream"`.</step>
    <step order="7">Add integration test: dispatch a playbook with null `sprk_configjson` → assert `NodeDestination = Chat`.</step>
    <step order="8">Add unit test for the primary-node selection heuristic.</step>
    <step order="9">Run `dotnet build` + tests; measure publish-size delta.</step>
    <step order="10">Quality gates per task-execute Step 9.5 (FULL rigor).</step>
    <step order="11">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 047 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Read">PlaybookDispatcher.cs + related repos</tool>
    <tool name="Edit">Apply changes + tests</tool>
    <tool name="Bash">dotnet build / test / publish</tool>
  </tools>

